name: Rosen Call Me Cards - Set of 100 Cards
description:
Make a statement with our professionally printed calling cards.  Besides looking ultra-chic, they will make your life easier when exchanging phone numbers + email addresses with friends, family, play-dates or networking!

• Printed on 110 pound, pearl coverstock
• Set of 100 cards (2" x 3.5")
• Card design is 2-sided
• Customize colors + fonts


**When placing order, please be sure to include all information for card in the notes section. Also specify color choices (we use PMS colors - many, many choices)

••• Please allow 3 business days to receive your proof. Please note - call me cards ship out 10-13 days after they are approved. They are professionally printed.•••
